As if that wasn't enough, today I'm announcing that I'm a judge of the best engagement photography with @junebugweddings . I never thought I would say something like this, but I will be able to review the amazing work of many photographers from all over the world. My heart is full.

These photos are from the shooting in Barcelona with The Process, the couple are @adrianaviteri and @alporllo thanks @elenaventura for making it possible.

Now to continue fulfilling dreams.

He tenido una de las semanas más intensas y divertidas de mi vida. Aún estoy con la resaca emocional de hablar delante de 800 personas en @bodaf, superando uno de mis mayores miedos, y haciéndolo junto a dos grandes amigos como @latxina o @serafin_castillo 

Y por supuesto @kitoli por ser mi sponsor y siempre apoyarme en todos los proyectos. 

Por si fuese poco, hoy anuncio que soy juez de la mejor fotografía de engagement junto a @junebugweddings . Nunca pensé que diría algo así, pero podré revisar el increíble trabajo de muchos fotógrafos de todo el mundo. Mi corazón está pleno.

Estás fotos son del shooting en Barcelona con @theprocess_curso , la parejaza son @adrianaviteri @alporllo gracias @evenmar por hacerlo posible.

Ahora a seguir cumpliendo sueños.

VIENNA. 2022. Lovers walking the streets. 

The process of discovering a new city with a couple is always demanding and exciting. This urban wedding was my first one in Austria, and I loved the light and the atmosphere all around. 

A series of three moments when I was amazed this day. ✨

Koh Samui. 2023. Dreams are real

In the last few years, I have made it a habit to start the season at the most distant wedding possible.

This year I could not miss the tradition. Koh Samui, an island paradise in the gulf of Thailand. 

Palm trees of an almost unreal greenery, and a sea that calls you and attracts you with its magnetism. I am still in a
Cloud when I think of the opportunities that this job is giving me, traveling and getting to know corners of the world that I had never even dreamed of. 

It is the beginning of a spectacular year. I will go to French castles in Provence, travel through the south of the USA and return to the magical island of Bali. Apart from Italy, Spain and some other magical trip that I can't reveal yet.

I've changed my color, by the way, and I'm in love, I hope you like it as much as I do. 

WP: @blisseventthailand

Koh Samui. 2023. Dreams are real

En los últimos años, he tomado por costumbre, comenzar la temporada en la boda mas lejana posible.

Este año no podía faltar a la tradición. Koh Samui, una isla paradisíaca en el golfo de Tailandia. 

Palmeras de un verdor casi irreal, y un mar que te llama y te atrae con su magnetismo. Aún sigo en una
Nube al pensar las oportunidades que me está dando este trabajo, Viajar y conocer rincones del mundo que ni siquiera hubiese soñado. 

Es el comienzo de un año espectacular. Iré a Castillos franceses en la Provenza, recorreré el sur de EEUU y volveré a la
Mágica isla de Bali. Aparte de Italia, España y algún que otro viaje mágico que aún no puedo desvelar.

He cambiado mi color, por cierto, y estoy enamorado, espero que os guste tanto como a mí. 

WP: @blisseventthailand
Vídeo: @korostudio

Dizziness in Ibiza. May 2023

Ibiza, it’s not only for partying. It’s also a powerful place for human connections. 

This year I have been already twice, and cannot wait to get back. The light, the breeze, the waves breaking in the old rocks. 

Lately I’m loving some movement in my photos. A feeling of dizziness. 2023 is just starting, wait for what’s coming!

Madonna. The beauty of lights and shades. 

Been always obsess with the dichotomy that moves the world and the universe.

I feel sometimes in living in a dream. And what a dream. 

Rhea & David romantic wedding last weekend was pure emotion. This is only the first sneak peak.

She had no name. It wasn't necessary in a world where everyone was intrinsically connected. 
Through her feet, she felt the heartbeat of every living thing in that desert. The sun and the moon guided her being like a magnet pulling iron.

Roots connected to her at night, crows protected her sleep. The dew bathed her lips just before dawn. 

She was a protector, a connector of worlds. Sometimes, legends said, she could be seen just before nightfall, as a spirit charged with one duty — protecting the desert. 

Model: @openthedoorevents 
Inspired by: @caramia @indiaearl & @jennifermoher ✨

Creating in Joshua Tree with @openthedoorevents just for the sake of it.

After an incredible workshop in #losangeles I felt the urge to create something in the desert. The concept was simple: a woman who represent a female spirit of the nature, a protector, a guide, a warrior.

Joshua tree is such an inspiring place. The energy moves all over under the ground. Those trees mesmerizing everyone, like a snake playing with its prey 🐍

Celeste & Neria ✨

Spinning around each other, like a whirlpool of water that accelerates and brings two ships irremediably closer together. 

The love of the two of them touched all of us who were present. The ceremony did not leave a single person without tears in their eyes. 

In life, sometimes everything intense comes together. On Friday, they celebrated their wonderful love for each other, and on Saturday, they received news about Israel that no one would have wanted to hear. 

Love is the only force that knows no borders. May a love as strong as theirs inspire many to follow their example. I adore you C & N.

Wedding by @openthedoorevents

It has been a long journey, and this is just the prologue of everything. I’m so grateful to be here doing what I love the most ✨

Sin duda alguna, el MAYOR MIEDO de cualquier fotógrafo o videografo es perder nuestro material.

Da igual si es por un descuido borrando nuestra tarjeta de memoria o porque el disco duro se corrompe, la situación es la misma; PÁNICO ABSOLUTO 😱 

Estando estos días en Bali formateé sin querer mis fotos del viaje, y no hace falta que os diga, es una sensación horrible.

Por suerte los amigos de @wondershare.recoverit tienen la solución para este tipo de situaciones. Su software te ayudará a recuperar archivos eliminados, corruptos o dañados, y sin perder nada de calidad…

Fotos, vídeos, música, lo que sea. Recuerdos o trabajos que podrás revivir con tres sencillos clicks. 

Os dejo el enlace para que lo podáis descargar gratis en mi link de la bio 👈🏽 Os aseguro que no os vais a arrepentir de tenerlo 🙏🏽

I’m not going to fool anyone. The first few times I heard about AI for selecting photos or editing, I dismissed it immediately. 

That was part of my creative process and I didn’t plan to bypass it. But little by little I experimented, and I realized that precisely, if I wanted to make time to be creative, I needed time for myself away from the computer screen.

Aftershoot has helped me not only to dedicate time to what really matters, but also to live the life I want to live. While selecting and editing the photos in my personal style.

Take advantage of Black Friday, and check out their offer to save time for yourself. No internet, no limits, just more freedom for you.

No voy a engañar a nadie. Las primeras veces que oí hablar de la IA para seleccionar fotos o editar, lo descarté de inmediato. 

Eso era parte de mi proceso creativo y no pensaba derivarlo. Pero poco a poco fui experimentando, y me dí cuenta de que precisamente, si quería sacar tiempo para ser creativo, necesitaba tiempo para mi alejado de la pantalla del ordenador.

Aftershoot, me ha ayudado no sólo a dedicarle tiempo a lo que verdaderamente importa, sino que además, puedo vivir la vida que me apetece vivir. Mientras selecciona y edita las fotos con mi estilo personal.

Aprovecha que están de Black Friday, y échale un ojo a su oferta para poder ganar tiempo para ti. Sin internet, sin límites, simplemente más libertad para ti.

Capturing the essence of love in
every delicate detail.
I bring to life the dreams of every
couple on their special day. My lens
focuses on the subtle nuances that
make your wedding uniquely yours
- the gentle clasp of hands, the soft
whispers, and the radiant smiles.
Let me immortalize your love story
in timeless photographs that speak
of hope, happiness, and eternal
love.
Ready to have your magical
moments captured? Reach out and
let’s create your forever memories
together. ✨

Wp: @openthedoorevents ✨

Get to know me: From a quiet
introvert lost in comic books and
tales from afar, I discovered a
world behind the lens where I
capture life‘s unscripted beauty. My
journey began as a street
photographer, silently observing
life‘s candid moments.
Ten years on, my approach
remains the same: letting
moments unfold naturally,
capturing their essence. Join me in
celebrating life‘s simple, yet
profound moments. 📸✨

Caught in a moment of pure bliss,
where time stands still and love
speaks louder than words.

Let me turn your love story into a
visual masterpiece that echoes
through time.

Season is over. 

10 countries, 28 couples, more than 7 workshops, hundreds of people that I meet. I’m incredibly grateful for everything this year gave me.

I’d love to tell you everything is coming in 2024, but let’s keep it as a secret for now. I’ll tell you soon.

The photo is from the first wedding of the year in Koh Samui, Thailand. And I think is a good representation of my year: constantly in motion ✨

Life is a journey. One to be spontaneous and unique. To live it fully without remorse or fear 🌴

Shannon and Jack decided that their path was going to be love, adventure and deeply rooted connections. 

Their elopement in Bali was magical. They committed to each other over the clouds, these are some of those moments.

2023, I will only say “thank you”. 

Universe is still proving to me how generous and creative can get. I have so much so be grateful for. I’ll keep manifesting for 2024 to get surprised.

Thank to every single one of you who pushed me to be a better version of myself: either because you love me or because you don’t. The result is still I’m becoming someone more connected to earth. 

Enjoy the ride 🙏🏽✨
